item.title: 第一篇博客
item.description: This is a closed book examination. Please place all your books on the floor beside you. You may keep one page of notes on your desktop in addition to this exam package. All Exams will be collected promptly at the end of the class period. Please be prepared to quickly hand in your examination at that time.
